General.Name: Locafy Ltd
General.Description: Locafy Limited develops online marketing software-as-a-service technology that publishes content on search engine optimized web pages for business owners in Australia, North America, and internationally. The company operates through two segments, Publishing and SEO Agency. It also provides publishing solutions that assists publishers to syndicate their citation content in a local search context through the company's online directories and for curated content, including business profile directory listings, bulk business profile directory listings, and enhanced listings. The company offers article accelerator, a search solution whereby content is published or republished. In addition, it owns and operates web pages related to business directories. Further, the company provides SEO solutions designed to gain online marketing prominence for specific keywords used for specific location, service area, and for national search terms for non-location specific products and services through local pages, proximity booster, and keyword maximizer. The company was formerly known as Moboom Limited and changed its name to Locafy Limited in January 2021. Locafy Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
